===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

{{liushu|p}}. The component [[戶]] (representing the shape of a shoulder) is combined with [[月]] (the radical of [[肉]], meaning "flesh" or "meat") to convey the meaning of "shoulder."<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

