===Etymology===
Cognate with {{cog|qfa-kms-pro|*k-xiːn¹||arm}}, {{cog|tai-pro|*qeːnᴬ||[[arm]]}} (whence {{cog|th|แขน||arm}}) ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Alternatively, possibly from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*k(w/y)an||[[shoulder]]}}.

